flowchart LR
  U[User] --> A[Agent (Claude Code / MCP client)]

  A -->|tool call| H[PreToolUse Hook / Router]
  H --> S[MCP Output Sandbox Server]

  S -->|spawn per-call| P[Isolated Subprocess
(runtime: py/js/sh/...) ]
  P -->|reads files / runs CLIs| FS[(Repo / OS / Auth CLIs)]

  P -->|raw artifacts stay here| ART[(Logs / Snapshots / CSV / API payloads)]
  P -->|stdout only (filtered/extracted)| S

  S -->|small extract| A
  A --> L[LLM]

  A -->|optional| KB[Index/Search Tool]
  KB --> DB[(SQLite FTS5
BM25 index)]
  KB -->|exact blocks| A
